I have worked with many financial professionals during the course of my career and I can state objectively that few matched the skill level that John possesses.  As a company, we always took pride in the quality and timeliness of our financial reporting actually receiving accolades from the Street for same.  This is in large measure to John’s credit.  I could rely on whatever set of financials John developed—each time and without question.  He developed an intimate knowledge of ATC’s businesses with a thorough understanding of the factors that drove the financials.  This was invaluable to me in being able to sucessfully run our businesses.  John developed financial models that would be the envy of any company and had a mastery of the puts and takes that drove changes to our financials like no other CFO with whom I have collaborated.  He drove the budgeting process, was vital to our M&A reviews, developed our SEC-mandated reports, and just overall knew the story behind every critical number ATC reported.  

John is a top-notch professional.  Suffice to say, I am grateful to John for his professional service to ATC and feel solidly confident in my recommendation of him for another CFO position.  Any organization would be proud to call John its CFO just as ATC was.  

